#  SAP R2R (Record-to-Report) Project

## Overview

This project demonstrates the complete Record-to-Report (R2R) cycle in SAP FI, including journal entries, ledger management, and financial reporting.

## Company Scenario

ABC Manufacturing Pvt. Ltd., a manufacturing firm, uses SAP FI for managing financial transactions and reporting.

## Process Flow

Journal Entry → General Ledger → Trial Balance → Profit & Loss → Balance Sheet

## Features

* Journal Entry Simulation
* Trial Balance Generation
* Profit & Loss Calculation
* Balance Sheet Generation

## Run Project

pip install -r requirements.txt
python simulation/main.py

## Screenshots

Refer to images/ folder

##  Learning Outcome

* SAP FI R2R understanding
* Financial reporting concepts
* Practical simulation

